wiki.summary: “FIND MY WAY” is DaBaby’s second single of 2020 following his February 2020 track, “SHUT UP,” and is also the lead single of his third studio album, BLAME IT ON BABY. The track is a stylistic change for DaBaby, as he sings on the chorus while still rapping on the song’s verses. He first teased this track with a video posted on Instagram on March 25, 2020. He then posted an acoustic remix video with Einer Bankz on March 30, premiering another expected verse from the song. Read more on Last.fm.
